title: 031109 - 032509 bridge pack
description:
Ladies and gentlemen, this torrent contains a combination of comic scans that were left over from the other packs that were posted over the past three release weeks. Of note is the inclusion of WildCATS v5 #8 which did not surface as a scan until this week when issue #9 was released.

There is still no sign of World of Warcraft #16.

Thanks to the scanners and the original sources who wish to remain nameless.

Please seed. Please enjoy.
